Workflows is a bold expansion. In four years, Snappr has become the leading=
 on-demand photography marketplace:=C2=A0
It=E2=80=99s processed over 120 million photos and edited more than 40 mill=
ion of them.=C2=A0
Its network covers 90% of the US population, 95% of Canada, 88% of the UK, =
and 77% of Australia, among others=C2=A0=C2=A0
Its revenue has grown at a 14% compound monthly growth rate (CMGR) since it=
