Its gross merchandise value (GMV) is in the tens of millions of dollars, an=
d it captures a strong percentage of that as revenue.=C2=A0
The company has raised $13 million and has only spent a fraction of it to a=
ccomplish all that.=C2=A0
The majority of the company=E2=80=99s revenue now comes from enterprise (tw=
