 broadly).
The company could have kept its head down and built a really nice photograp=
hy marketplace business. Instead, it=E2=80=99s taking all of the resources =
it=E2=80=99s built up and launching Snappr Workflows, its SaaS and API prod=
uct aimed at the enterprise clients who demand it and the mid-market client=
s Snappr hasn=E2=80=99t yet been able to serve.=C2=A0
The secret to Snappr=E2=80=99s success is that the Shoots business feeds th=
e Workflows business, in four main ways:=C2=A0
Solves the Chicken and Egg Problem for Enterprises. Enterprises need nation=
al supply (photographers and editors) overnight, which is impossible to bui=
ld on its own. When they call, you need to be ready, or you blow your chanc=
e. So you might try to build up the supply network ahead of demand, but the=
n supply gets burned waiting around with no work. Self-service demand fills=
 the gap.=C2=A0
Self-Service Increases Liquidity. The higher density the bookings are in an=
 area, the stronger the network effects. There=E2=80=99s more supply densit=
y, less photographer travel time, and a greater chance of matching the righ=
t photographer to the right booking.=C2=A0
Keeps Photographers Happy. Most photographers like being able to mix it up =
and do B2C and enterprise shoots in the same day.=C2=A0
Shoots is the Biggest Channel for Workflows. 48% of Workflows enterprise cu=
stomers today made a self-service booking with Shoots before becoming Workf=
lows customers.
This last point is where that lovely acronym =E2=80=93 B2C2B2PLG - comes fr=
om: people who book Shoots, both as consumers and for their businesses, end=
 up becoming the fuel for Snappr=E2=80=99s Workflows product-led growth eng=
ine and often grow into larger enterprise accounts.
And Workflows is a game changer for Snappr=E2=80=99s business. It turns the=
 product from on-demand to API-first, like a Zapier for the visual content =
pipeline. Snappr=E2=80=99s story is an accidental playbook for building an =
API-first business, backwards. So today, we=E2=80=99ll dive into the evolut=
ion by covering:=C2=A0
