iv><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0 0 1em 0;">Every big API-first business looks like it&#8217;s just softwar=
e &#8211; just a few lines of code &#8211; until you look under the hood. T=
here, you&#8217;ll find all sorts of complexity. Abstracting it away is the=
 API&#8217;s raison d&#8217;&#234;tre.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Most API-first giants, l=
ike Stripe, Twilio, and Plaid, start with the software and realize that get=
ting the software right actually requires a lot of undercover schlep.&nbsp;=
</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 1em 0;"><a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOwyAQ-5pyjH=
